for disaster relief or border inspection

284
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:58,660
but actually, they were kicked out of the court

285
00:16:58,740 --> 00:16:59,940
and suspended from their previous posts

286
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:00,820
to halt the reform.

287
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:02,180
As the Prime Minister,

288
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:04,820
he didn’t say anything in order to protect himself.

289
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,620
Other than that,

290
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:12,540
you know he proposed

291
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:13,820
that Ouyang Xiu should be transferred
out of the Capital?

292
00:17:15,820 --> 00:17:17,540
Yongshu remonstrated with His Majesty

293
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:18,820
about overly promoting

294
00:17:18,820 --> 00:17:19,980
Empress Dowager Zhangyi’s family.

295
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:23,940
So, to pander to His Majesty,

296
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:25,540
he stepped on Yongshu.

297
00:17:27,340 --> 00:17:29,140
If we don’t take any action,

298
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:30,460
won’t we be the same as him?

299
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,020
Since Ouyang Xiu left the Capital,

300
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:43,140
disagreements and criticisms

301
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:44,620
have been flooding in.

302
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:47,620
Sun Fu’s and Cai Xiang’s are extremely sharp.

303
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:50,140
They condemned Xia Song, me

304
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:53,260
and called Mr. Yan evil.

305
00:17:54,060 --> 00:17:56,220
They praised the Eighth Prince

306
00:17:56,220 --> 00:17:57,220
for telling the truth before death.

307
00:17:58,340 --> 00:18:00,860
Loyalty and honesty are really...

308
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,260
Never mind.

309
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:07,660
Once Zuixinglai’s death is made public,

310
00:18:08,020 --> 00:18:09,700
they’ll no longer focus on Ouyang Xiu.

311
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:13,180
The fight among officials will stop

312
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:15,540
and they’ll unitedly advise me

313
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:18,540
to adopt sons again.

314
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:22,700
Your Majesty...

315
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:24,780
That’s understandable.

316
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:26,940
But

317
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:30,060
I don’t want Mr. Yan

318
00:18:30,940 --> 00:18:32,900
to join them to persuade me.

319
00:18:35,940 --> 00:18:36,980
He was the one

320
00:18:37,540 --> 00:18:39,500
telling me not to meet with my birth mother.

321
00:18:40,300 --> 00:18:41,420
When I meant to go to the battlefield,

322
00:18:41,740 --> 00:18:43,460
he accused me of being heirless.

323
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:47,660
Yan Shu is sophisticated.

324
00:18:50,340 --> 00:18:53,700
Is he?

325
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:15,900
Who died?

326
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:17,260
Who is this grand funeral for?

327
00:19:17,780 --> 00:19:18,860
The Eighth Prince.

328
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,740
When he was in critical condition,

329
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,500
His Majesty had him treated

330
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:24,340
in the palace.

331
00:19:24,340 --> 00:19:25,620
Of course his funeral is grand.

332
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,660
Cai Xiang’s proposal.

333
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:35,860
Sun Fu’s proposal.

334
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,300
This...

335
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:44,460
Do you remember this, Mr. Yan?

336
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:56,020
Lofty are the Five Mountains.
Jade is from Mount Kunlun.

337
00:19:57,020 --> 00:20:00,300
Vast are the Four Waters.
Gold is found in River Li.

338
00:20:02,220 --> 00:20:05,300
I wrote this eulogy

339
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:07,020
for Empress Dowager Zhangyi.

340
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,140
This eulogy

341
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:18,100
is beautifully written with profound meanings.

342
00:20:18,740 --> 00:20:20,420
It praises the two Empress Dowagers

343
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:22,780
without revealing my background.

344
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:25,460
Your analogies are excellent.

345
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:26,740
But one thing

346
00:20:30,180 --> 00:20:31,180
is missing.

347
00:20:34,060 --> 00:20:35,980
That is honesty.

348
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:40,820
I knew who Your Majesty’s biological mother is

349
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:43,260
but I didn’t say anything.

350
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:46,020
I’m disloyal

351
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:49,740
by deceiving Your Majesty.

352
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:54,660
Why didn’t you defend yourself?

353
00:20:57,620 --> 00:21:01,820
I’m not a blunt person.

354
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:04,900
Had it been Fan Zhongyan or Ouyang Xiu,

355
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:08,980
they wouldn’t have written like this.

356
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:21,700
But I chose you.

357
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:24,940
Back then...

358
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,220
Back then,

359
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:31,220
I wasn’t ignorant.

360
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,420
They didn’t know the whole truth

361
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:36,660
and assumed you lied to me.

362
00:21:37,260 --> 00:21:38,700
I didn’t know the truth

363
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,900
until the Empress Dowager passed away.

364
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:46,460
But I know you well.

365
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,900
Had you been disloyal, why

366
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:51,460
would you have acted against the Empress Dowager

367
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:53,620
when I was young?

368
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:57,140
Why would you have pointed out that I had no son

369
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,260
to stop me from joining the battle

370
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:01,500
at the risk of infuriating me?

371
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:17,580
Mr. Yan, you should leave the Capital

372
00:22:20,140 --> 00:22:24,220
to govern Yingzhou as the Minister of Works.

373
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:30,260
Thank you for Your Majesty’s generosity.

374
00:22:37,820 --> 00:22:39,580
Is that sarcasm?

375
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:42,100
I understand

376
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:45,660
you are protecting me, Your Majesty.

377
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:48,300
Yingzhou is wealthy.

378
00:22:49,020 --> 00:22:51,060
Schools there, state-run or private-run,

379
00:22:51,220 --> 00:22:53,220
aren’t as good as those in Shangqiu or Kaifeng.

380
00:22:54,300 --> 00:22:55,980
The excesses are reduced slowly

381
00:22:56,980 --> 00:23:00,580
but educating the public can continue.

382
00:23:01,740 --> 00:23:05,500
It’ll benefit generations to come.

383
00:23:13,340 --> 00:23:15,060
Ouyang Xiu might not understand

384
00:23:15,740 --> 00:23:17,220
your intention to get him

385
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:18,220
out of the Capital

386
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:22,980
but you always understand me well.

387
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:29,500
Actually,

388
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:34,100
there’s one more thing.

389
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:50,340
My son,

390
00:23:52,980 --> 00:23:57,300
no, the heir of Song,

391
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:01,140
your future emperor...

392
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:02,980
He...

393
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,340
left us.

394
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:44,340
Prime Minister Yan.

395
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,020
Prime Minister Yan.

396
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:48,460
What happened today

397
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:51,060
is unfair to you, Prime Minister Yan.

398
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,420
How could they rake up the past

399
00:24:53,420 --> 00:24:55,100
and use it against you now?

400
00:24:55,620 --> 00:24:56,780
Obviously,

401
00:24:57,060 --> 00:24:59,260
they intended to harm you.

402
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:02,660
That eulogy was written 11 years ago.

403
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:04,700
Nobody said anything then,

404
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:07,460
but now,

405
00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:09,700
it’s regarded as the proof of your disloyalty.

406
00:25:09,860 --> 00:25:10,700
Unbelievable!

407
00:25:11,020 --> 00:25:12,700
It’s the pretext

408
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:15,500
for taking revenge for their clique.

409
00:25:17,060 --> 00:25:18,380
They were disgruntled

410
00:25:18,380 --> 00:25:19,940
at Fu Bi’s and Ouyang Xiu’s demotion

411
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:22,180
but they had nothing on you.

412
00:25:22,940 --> 00:25:24,540
So they dug up

413
00:25:24,540 --> 00:25:26,500
the eulogy for the Empress Dowager to attack you.

414
00:25:27,020 --> 00:25:29,340
Shame on them!

415
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:35,620
His Majesty

416
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:38,260
trusted Fu Bi and assigned him

417
00:25:38,580 --> 00:25:40,500
to relieve the people in disaster.

418
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:43,180
That shows His Majesty’s kindness.

419
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:47,060
I suggested Ouyang Xiu
should be transferred to Hedong

420
00:25:47,060 --> 00:25:48,100
to assist Fu Bi

421
00:25:48,820 --> 00:25:50,020
in accordance with

422
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:51,820
His Majesty’s benevolence.

423
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:54,260
How is that a demotion

424
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:56,860
or revenge?

425
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:08,300
My own kitchen made this congee

426
00:26:08,740 --> 00:26:10,020
with five kinds of grains,

427
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:12,660
wolfberries from Tibet

428
00:26:13,100 --> 00:26:14,820
and osmanthus sugar.

429
00:26:15,940 --> 00:26:17,300
When I was little and fell ill,

430
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:19,540
my mother would make this for me.

431
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:22,300
She said it could nourish my body.

432
00:26:22,300 --> 00:26:23,220
Have a taste, Your Majesty.

433
00:26:30,020 --> 00:26:30,740
Very good.

434
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:33,180
I’ll tell Lusi to copy the recipe

435
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,340
and bring it to your chamber.

436
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:41,820
No need.

437
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:43,740
Others can’t cook it well.

438
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:46,100
I’ll come here

439
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:47,980
to eat this.

440
00:26:49,420 --> 00:26:50,260
From now on,

441
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:53,300
I’ll have breakfast with you every other day.

442
00:26:56,140 --> 00:26:57,460
Your Majesty, you are too busy.

443
00:26:57,740 --> 00:26:58,980
Don’t worry about me.

444
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:01,340
Really?

445
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:02,260
I hope we can

446
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,340
have breakfast together more often.

447
00:27:03,540 --> 00:27:04,620
Father, you know,

448
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:06,540
mother always cooked for me and...

449
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,540
Let me bring you

450
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:17,140
the plums I made.

451
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:37,420
I’ll come here more.

452
00:27:38,940 --> 00:27:40,060
I’ll spend more time with you.

453
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:45,620
To me,

454
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:48,580
this place feels like home the most.

455
00:27:51,820 --> 00:27:52,780
Here

456
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:57,060
I can have fun without worries.

457
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:02,820
But I need to take care of

458
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:05,140
all sorts of problems and troubles first.

459
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,260
Only when I couldn’t continue

460
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,620
would I allow myself to come here to rest.

461
00:28:12,900 --> 00:28:14,300
I never thought

462
00:28:15,380 --> 00:28:16,900
my sweet home

463
00:28:19,140 --> 00:28:21,220
would be shattered

464
00:28:23,100 --> 00:28:24,420
beyond repair.

465
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,460
I’ve failed

466
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:29,820
to spend enough quality time

467
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:31,100
with the three of you

468
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:34,620
and I won’t do it again

469
00:28:34,620 --> 00:28:35,660
to you two

470
00:28:35,660 --> 00:28:36,780
to leave more regrets.

471
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:12,020
Mr. Han.

472
00:29:14,900 --> 00:29:15,780
Prime Minister Yan,

473
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:17,500
you’re only bringing Jidao to Yingzhou?

474
00:29:18,380 --> 00:29:19,900
He’s too naughty.

475
00:29:20,140 --> 00:29:21,340
Without me at home,

476
00:29:21,380 --> 00:29:22,700
he can lie to his grandmother and mother

477
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:24,060
as he pleases

478
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:25,460
and drives his teacher away,

479
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:27,620
so I have to bring him with me

480
00:29:27,980 --> 00:29:29,100
to teach him myself.

481
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:32,420
Board the boat with Uncle An first.

482
00:29:34,060 --> 00:29:34,940
Yes.

483
00:29:36,340 --> 00:29:38,460
= Yan Jidao =

484
00:29:44,620 --> 00:29:46,300
He must be talented

485
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:47,380
in your eyes,

486
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:49,100
so you don’t trust others to teach him

487
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:50,140
other than yourself.

488
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:52,260
I do favor him more

489
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:55,060
not because he can achieve something big.

490
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:56,780
He doesn’t like reading

491
00:29:56,980 --> 00:29:58,500
educational books

492
00:29:59,020 --> 00:30:01,020
but prefers art, especially music.

493
00:30:01,300 --> 00:30:02,820
He can think outside the box

494
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:05,060
and surprise me with his words occasionally.

495
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:07,460
Now, I realize

496
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:09,220
there’s nothing more important

497
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:12,340
than seeing him enjoying

498
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,700
a happy and carefree life.

499
00:30:17,660 --> 00:30:19,300
If your mother and wife

500
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:21,100
need any help in the Capital, they...

501
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:23,460
We’ll leave first.

502
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:25,780
They’ll sell the house in the Capital

503
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:27,180
and pack up.

504
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:29,700
My second and third sons will escort

505
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:32,060
their grandmother, mother and younger sister

506
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:34,100
back to our hometown Fuzhou in Jiangxi Province.

507
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,820
Sell the house?

508
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:40,740
Why?

509
00:30:41,700 --> 00:30:43,500
Your other two sons are working in the Capital.

510
00:30:44,180 --> 00:30:46,020
His Majesty trusts Fu Bi.

511
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:48,940
I’m different from them.

512
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:52,660
I won’t come back here.

513
00:30:56,060 --> 00:30:57,540
You should reconsider it.

514
00:30:58,700 --> 00:30:59,700
His Majesty

515
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:01,300
removed you from the Prime Minister

516
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:02,580
due to a decade-old incident.

517
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:04,620
Cai and Sun

518
00:31:04,620 --> 00:31:05,540
used that against you

519
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,260
only to vent their anger.

520
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:09,700
Even they couldn’t believe

521
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:11,140
His Majesty accepted their advice.

522
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:14,300
His Majesty’s intention is unclear

523
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,820
but all these years,

524
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:18,260
he clearly trusts and depends on you

525
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,420
the most.

526
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:23,300
His Majesty has no one to depend on.

527
00:31:23,700 --> 00:31:24,740
All emperors in history

528
00:31:25,020 --> 00:31:26,500
are loners.

529
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:29,580
That applies to us, too.

530
00:31:30,380 --> 00:31:31,460
Speaking of that,

531
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:33,740
what supports His Majesty, you, me

532
00:31:34,620 --> 00:31:36,100
and everyone here

533
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:40,260
is nothing but a stable

534
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:42,260
and peaceful nation.

535
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:56,020
Your Highness, what did Imperial Physicians say?

536
00:31:59,460 --> 00:32:01,940
They said Madam Feng will give birth

537
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:03,900
in a few days.

538
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:06,340
The position of the fetus is good.

539
00:32:07,180 --> 00:32:09,100
Madam Feng is healthy, too.

540
00:32:09,940 --> 00:32:10,940
If it goes smoothly,

541
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:13,260
she and the baby should be fine.

542
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:19,180
What’s wrong?

543
00:32:20,420 --> 00:32:21,420
I meant

544
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:23,420
if they took your pulse.

545
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:27,180
Me?

546
00:32:30,060 --> 00:32:31,660
They already took it last time.

547
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:32,500
I’m fine.

548
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,180
I called them

549
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:35,460
to know about Madam Feng’s condition

550
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:36,780
and the Eighth Princess’s.

551
00:32:38,220 --> 00:32:40,060
She’s been weak since she was born.

552
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,420
Lately, her condition’s worsened.

553
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:42,820
Physicians hummed and hawed.

554
00:32:45,660 --> 00:32:47,380
Madam Zhang is having monks

555
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:48,740
chanting the sutra every day.

556
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:51,300
I hope she will be fine.

557
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:55,060
Why are you only caring about others?

558
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,860
You seem fine

559
00:32:58,340 --> 00:32:59,540
but still cough at night.

560
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,380
You should be checked by physicians again

561
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:02,420
to be relieved.

562
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,820
Only if Madam Feng gives birth to a son

563
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:09,140
will I truly be relieved.

564
00:33:10,820 --> 00:33:13,100
His Majesty’s only son died.

565
00:33:13,780 --> 00:33:15,420
Once news gets out,

566
00:33:15,820 --> 00:33:18,460
proposals will soon roll in,

567
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:22,140
persuading him to adopt sons.

568
00:33:23,100 --> 00:33:24,500
He lost his only son,

569
00:33:25,500 --> 00:33:26,540
but those officials

570
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:29,420
are only concerned that the state is heirless.

571
00:33:31,060 --> 00:33:32,300
He can’t even mourn

572
00:33:32,300 --> 00:33:33,700
his son’s death.

573
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:36,780
And the Eighth Princess...

574
00:33:39,620 --> 00:33:44,540
By downsizing officials,

575
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:47,220
combating corruption and promoting the reform,

576
00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:49,180
achievements have been made

577
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:51,380
but there are threats under the water.

578
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:54,060
Opponents are still many.

579
00:33:55,580 --> 00:33:56,540
In the palace,

580
00:33:57,380 --> 00:33:58,980
the only prince

581
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:00,540
and three princesses died in a row.

582
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,940
Other than

583
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:04,740
those vicious speculations,

584
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:07,580
I can’t image how heartbroken

585
00:34:08,220 --> 00:34:09,620
His Majesty is.

586
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:15,780
His Majesty accused Your Highness

587
00:34:15,780 --> 00:34:17,500
of only caring about the state

588
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:18,980
and your responsibility as the Empress.

589
00:34:20,580 --> 00:34:21,340
Actually,

590
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:25,220
you act like that because you know

591
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:28,260
His Majesty and the state

592
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,780
are a whole.

593
00:34:31,700 --> 00:34:34,140
Your Highness’s heart is filled with His Majesty,

594
00:34:35,020 --> 00:34:36,260
meaning the state

595
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,860
also fills your heart.

596
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:46,260
Prime Minister Yan,

597
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:52,100
I’m overwhelmed.

598
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:53,940
I don’t know what to do next.

599
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:57,940
Among officials leading the reform,

600
00:34:58,700 --> 00:35:00,300
only you

601
00:35:00,620 --> 00:35:01,620
are still in the Cabinet.

602
00:35:02,700 --> 00:35:03,940
The three excesses have been lessened.

603
00:35:04,620 --> 00:35:07,220
Those suffering huge losses are pushing back.

604
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,580
To restore the balance,

605
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:11,820
His Majesty will slower or suspend the reform

606
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,540
to make necessary adjustments.

607
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:15,020
I understand that.

608
00:35:15,740 --> 00:35:17,380
I’m not clinging on to the reform

609
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:20,260
but right now, His Majesty

610
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,860
is surrounded by officials

611
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:23,140
like Jia Changchao and Xia Song.

612
00:35:23,660 --> 00:35:26,380
The loyal are replaced by the corrupted.

613
00:35:27,260 --> 00:35:28,820
Losses of the wild Ouyang Yongshu

614
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:30,500
and the blunt Fan Xiwen

615
00:35:31,220 --> 00:35:33,420
aren’t too big,

616
00:35:34,180 --> 00:35:35,100
but Prime Minister Yan,

617
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:37,540
you always put the greater good first

618
00:35:37,540 --> 00:35:38,420
to ensure the balance.

619
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,300
Yet His Majesty...

620
00:35:39,380 --> 00:35:40,100
Jidao,

621
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:41,940
behave yourself!

622
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:43,580
Don’t fall into the water.

623
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:46,900
I’m going to learn swimming in Yingzhou.

624
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,660
Both His Majesty and the masses

625
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:56,780
are longing for a stable

626
00:35:56,780 --> 00:35:58,380
and peaceful nation.

627
00:35:59,620 --> 00:36:00,500
His Majesty

628
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:03,820
allows loyal officials

629
00:36:04,340 --> 00:36:05,540
to act against his will

630
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:07,100
for that purpose.

631
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:10,980
He tolerates the mediocre and the corrupted

632
00:36:11,260 --> 00:36:12,860
yapping before him

633
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:14,660
also for that purpose.

634
00:36:18,020 --> 00:36:18,740
Zhigui,

635
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:21,500
I chose to serve the court

636
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:24,580
not to be remembered by history.

637
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:27,460
All my previous dissuasion

638
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:30,180
was part of my job.

639
00:36:32,140 --> 00:36:33,220
I’m old.

640
00:36:34,660 --> 00:36:36,220
After so many years of service,

641
00:36:38,860 --> 00:36:41,700
I can live with a clear conscience.

642
00:37:32,940 --> 00:37:41,020
♪ Life will end eventually ♪

643
00:37:41,020 --> 00:37:47,210
♪ Every separation is sorrowful ♪

644
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:51,100
Mr. Yan, are you teaching me plum blossom poems?

645
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:52,220
You once told me

646
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:55,100
lotus and plum blossoms are kings of flowers.

647
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:56,580
They top others with their elegance.

648
00:37:56,740 --> 00:37:59,460
Lotus after the rain and plum blossoms
in the snow are the best.

649
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:02,100
Good verses are inspired by nature.

650
00:38:02,700 --> 00:38:05,340
We aren’t going to study them today.

651
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:06,940
Let’s enjoy their fragrance in the snow.

652
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:09,260
We can pick some flowers

653
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,740
and collect snow on the petals.

654
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:13,140
Tell the kitchen to make tea with the snow

655
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:16,060
and bake pastries stuffed with flowers.

656
00:38:17,300 --> 00:38:18,940
Pastries stuffed with flowers?

657
00:38:20,393 --> 00:38:28,460
♪ Grieve over falling flowers and short spring ♪

658
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:33,220
♪ Better treasure the ones you still have instead ♪

659
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:34,300
What about my mother,

660
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,740
the one who carried me for ten months

661
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,220
but I didn’t get

662
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:39,500
to bow to once?

663
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:44,940
Mr. Yan.

664
00:38:48,780 --> 00:38:49,860
You’re back, Mr. Yan.

665
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:20,980
= Yan Shu passed away in 1055 A.D. =

666
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:23,820
= Court adjourned for two days =

667
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:27,380
= His stone tablet
is headed by “Former Imperial Tutor” =

668
00:39:48,740 --> 00:39:49,420
Mr. Zhang.

669
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:50,860
What brings you here today?

670
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:51,860
Please go upstairs.

671
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:53,020
I’m out to run an errand

672
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:53,860
and need to bring food and desserts

673
00:39:53,860 --> 00:39:55,020
back to the palace.

674
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,980
How’s your business?

675
00:39:59,060 --> 00:40:00,220
With the help

676
00:40:00,220 --> 00:40:01,340
of those 3,000 taels from the court

677
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,100
to buy the restaurant,

678
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:03,700
and thanks to the stability these years,

679
00:40:03,940 --> 00:40:04,820
I’ve finally paid off the tax

680
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:05,940
the previous owner owed.

681
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:09,140
Your room is on the second floor.

682
00:40:09,620 --> 00:40:11,860
It’s the best place to overlook the entire city

683
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:14,060
and enjoy songs and dances inside.

684
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:15,700
You can give me dividends

685
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,260
for my investment.

686
00:40:17,780 --> 00:40:19,060
I seldom come here.

687
00:40:19,220 --> 00:40:20,180
No need

688
00:40:20,180 --> 00:40:21,660
to empty a room for me.

689
00:40:21,780 --> 00:40:23,100
You’ll lose money.

690
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:26,620
Guests here all know

691
00:40:27,340 --> 00:40:28,740
you have a room here,

692
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:30,140
so no one dares

693
00:40:30,140 --> 00:40:31,380
to cause me trouble.

694
00:40:33,420 --> 00:40:36,100
You’re using me as a shield.

695
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,540
This way, please.

696
00:40:46,140 --> 00:40:46,860
Mr. Zhang.

697
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:07,020
Are you alright?

698
00:41:07,260 --> 00:41:10,300
= Bitao =

699
00:41:10,300 --> 00:41:11,060
Mr. Zhang,

700
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:12,940
she can’t speak.

701
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:14,700
My adopted mother brought her back from the market.

702
00:41:14,980 --> 00:41:16,380
When my adopted mother saw her,
she was sick and hungry

703
00:41:16,780 --> 00:41:17,900
and was beaten by a waiter for stealing buns.

704
00:41:18,260 --> 00:41:19,780
My adopted mother pitied her and brought her back.

705
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:21,180
She’s hardworking

706
00:41:21,420 --> 00:41:22,220
but timid.

707
00:41:22,220 --> 00:41:23,340
She’s afraid of strangers.

708
00:41:23,580 --> 00:41:24,460
You can leave.

709
00:41:24,940 --> 00:41:26,220
Take the order to the kitchen

710
00:41:26,380 --> 00:41:27,660
and tell them to prepare the food quickly.

711
00:41:27,740 --> 00:41:29,100
Ask Deshun to bring

712
00:41:29,100 --> 00:41:30,660
fresh fruit and liquor, too.

713
00:41:43,100 --> 00:41:44,140
When did she

714
00:41:46,660 --> 00:41:48,460
come here?

715
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:48,060
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

716
00:42:49,380 --> 00:42:57,740
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

717
00:43:00,580 --> 00:43:05,300
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

718
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:10,420
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

719
00:43:11,860 --> 00:43:17,340
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

720
00:43:17,340 --> 00:43:22,140
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

721
00:43:25,820 --> 00:43:31,460
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

722
00:43:31,460 --> 00:43:36,340
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

723
00:43:36,860 --> 00:43:42,620
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

724
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:47,700
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

725
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:53,060
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

726
00:43:53,700 --> 00:43:58,540
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

727
00:43:59,220 --> 00:44:04,380
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

728
00:44:04,860 --> 00:44:09,900
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

729
00:44:10,460 --> 00:44:14,540
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

730
00:44:15,980 --> 00:44:20,620
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

731
00:44:21,660 --> 00:44:26,820
♪ The howling wind ♪

732
00:44:27,180 --> 00:44:31,260
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

733
00:44:32,740 --> 00:44:37,660
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

734
00:44:38,300 --> 00:44:43,540
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

735
00:44:43,940 --> 00:44:49,220
♪ The howling wind ♪

736
00:44:49,540 --> 00:44:54,420
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

737
00:44:55,020 --> 00:45:01,740
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
